1
00:00:03,966 --> 00:00:07,000
The golden dream is getting restless.

2
00:00:09,300 --> 00:00:16,000
In the coming long nights, I'm afraid you will face many setbacks and witness many tragedies.

3
00:00:17,666 --> 00:00:22,600
And in the end, you will only see in black and white.

4
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:33,700
But please believe me that in that monochrome world, there will be a glimpse of fleeting red, and when you make a choice...

5
00:00:34,933 --> 00:00:36,700
...it will appear once more.

6
00:00:54,966 --> 00:01:01,933
What you must do, is ponder its significance, then return to the waking world.

7
00:01:07,900 --> 00:01:10,833
That's where we all find our answers.

